title: Highway/Rail Transfer Facilities that Contain Autoramps, USA, 1998
name: Highway/Rail Transfer Facilities that Contain Autoramps, USA, 1998
description:
This dataset displays the point location of Highway/Rail Transfer locations throughout the United States that contain an Auto Ramp. This data was formatted according to the longitude and the latitude coordinates for each location. This data was collected from the Bureau of Transportation Statistics http://www.bts.gov/publications/north_american_transportation_atlas_data/
and was accessed on January 29, 2008.
